nd One I'm not Listening To. http://t.co/M6xTHRcpPw *(18:39:00)*<a name=\"giftttdy\"></a>##### Twitter Mentions* @doghousemike Me Too, Thanks Mike :). *(Mentioned by ssx)* *(12:27:00)** @doghousemike @SandMshitter that&#8217;s Good to Hear! if Everything Goes as Planned I&#8217;ll Be much Better off :). *(Mentioned by ssx)* *(12:48:00)*<a name=\"giftttdy\"></a>","lines":[13,14],"size":2792,"outlinks":[],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
